5 Air, 30 Earth, 30 Fire
Basic mana cost: 600

This weave damages everything in the room that is not 
grouped with the caster, doing 3000 + (5 X Level) + (500 
per guildee in group other than caster) + (1d50 per 400 
mana added) points of damage.

NOTE: There is a small chance of this weave backfiring
and affecting the caster. It is suggested that you keep
subdue on while using this weave in order to avoid 
killing yourself.
