  <ghelp keyword="Test-Skill">
    <entry>&amp;CTEST-SKILL&amp;n

Usage: test player

This skill allows you to determine if a player can channel
and how strong or weak they are compaired to you.
What the different messages of test actually means, the 
numbers being the difference from your own strength:

&quot;very weak indeed. Perhaps a beginner.&quot; 0-5
&quot;far weaker than you.&quot;                  5-10%
&quot;a good deal weaker than you.&quot;          10%-30%
&quot;weaker than you.&quot;                      30%-45%
&quot;about half as strong as you.&quot;          45%-55%
&quot;a little weaker than you.&quot;             55%-70%
&quot;slightly weaker than you.&quot;             70%-85%
&quot;almost as strong as you.&quot;              85%-95%
&quot;about the same in strength.&quot;           95%-105%
&quot;a tiny bit stronger than you.&quot;         105%-115%
&quot;slightly stronger than you.&quot;           115%-145%
&quot;a little stronger than you.&quot;           145%-180%
&quot;about twice as strong as you.&quot;         180%-220%
&quot;stronger than you.&quot;                    220%-300%
&quot;a good deal stronger than you.&quot;        300%-1000%
&quot;far stronger than you!&quot;                1000%&lt;
</entry>
